  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have learned to draw on the power of the Unformed Maze, gaining the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Darkness.</strong> You can expend 1 Focus Point to cast the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplDarkness00]{Darkness} spell without spell components. You can see within the spell's area when you cast it with this feature. While the spell persists, you can move its area of Darkness to a space within 60 feet of yourself at the start of each of your turns.</p><p><strong>Pass Without Trace.</strong> You can expend 2 Focus Points to cast the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplPassWithou]{Pass Without Trace} spell without spell components.</p><p><strong>Silence.</strong> You can expend 2 Focus Points to cast the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplSilence000]{Silence} spell without spell components.</p><p><strong>Darkvision.</strong> You gain &amp;Reference[Darkvision] with a range of 60 feet. If you already have Darkvision, its range increases by 60 feet.</p><p><strong>Shadowy Figments.</strong> You know the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplMinorIllus]{Minor Illusion} spell. Wisdom is your spellcasting ability for it.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-p0chbgv6RivGmX1i\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Expend Focus Point</strong> and <strong>Expend 2 Focus Points</strong> activities expend the focus points and you can then use the spells which are granted to you at this level.</p><p>This feature includes an Active Effect that increases your Darkvision.</p><p>You are granted the Minor Illusion spell when you reach this level.</p></section>",
      "chat": ""
    },
